{
  "texts": [
    "Moreover, the veracity of information seems to be sometimes negotiable for the sake of profit, as the competition is increasingly tough (Fraga-Lamas and Fernández-Caramés 2020).",
    "At the same time, we have witnessed tremendous advancements in the field of Artificial Intelligence (AI) (especially Deep Learning (DL)), Big Data and cloud computing.",
    "This powerful technology combination is able to provide real-time data-driven intelligence, leveraging large amounts of collected data into useful information.",
    "Thanks to these advances, together with those in image processing, the concept of Deepfake has appeared.",
    "It can be defined as the generation of fake digital content or manipulation of genuine one through the use of DL techniques.The content includes video, image, audio, and text among other sources."
  ]
}